<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Panther Training Club - Trainer Home</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A cool thing made with Glitch">
    <link id="favicon" rel="icon" href="https://glitch.com/edit/favicon-app.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
   
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.2.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-GJzZqFGwb1QTTN6wy59ffF1BuGJpLSa9DkKMp0DgiMDm4iYMj70gZWKYbI706tWS" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1c2841, #273c5a, #2d4873, #31538b, #345da2);
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 70px; 
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: transparent !important;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000; 
            padding: 10px 0;
            
          
        }
        .navbar-brand img {
            height: 50px; 
        }
        .navbar-toggler-icon,
        .navbar-brand,
        .nav-link {
            color: #fff !important;
        }
        .navbar a.navbar-brand:hover,
        .navbar a.nav-link:hover {
            color: #ddd !important; 
        }
      
        .footer {
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .content-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .content-section h2 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content-section p {
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px; 
        }

        /* Style for the main box container */
        .box-container {
            background-color: #f0f0f0; 
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-style: solid;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex; 
            flex-wrap: wrap; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
        }

       
        .box-container h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000; 
            width: 100%; 
        }

        /* Style for paragraph text */
        .box-container p {
            margin: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #000; 
            width: 48%;
            box-sizing: border-box; 
            padding: 0 10px; 
        }
      
    </style>
</head>
<body class="container">

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light fixed-top">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/trainerhome">
                <img src="https://cdn.glitch.global/053c29cd-dfdc-43c1-80f1-bb5086f7c78a/Panther.png?v=1714432585127" alt="Panther Training Club Logo">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a style="color:black;" class="nav-link" href="trainerhome">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a style="color:black;" class="nav-link" href="trainerprofile"> View/Update Profile&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
                    </li>
                    
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <button class="btn btn-light" onclick="logout()">Logout</button>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 id="trainerName"></h2>
            <p>As a dedicated fitness professional, you play a vital role in helping individuals achieve their health and wellness goals.</p>
            <p>Stay organized and manage your appointments efficiently with our booking system. Keep track of your clients and communicate effectively to provide them with the best possible experience.</p>

            <div class="box-container" id="detailsContainer">
                <!-- Member and booking details will be dynamically added here -->
            </div>
          
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <span>Â© 2024 Panther Training Club. All rights reserved.</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script>
      function logout() {
            localStorage.removeItem('membertoken');
            localStorage.removeItem('memberId');
            window.location.href = '/index';
        }

      
    </script>
    <script src="trainerhome.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
